@pleerock This seems to still be an issue unfortunately, unless you specifically specify the type.

This won't work:

```ts
  @Column()
  type: PlatformType;
```

But this will:

```ts
  @Column({
    type: 'enum',
    enum: PlatformType,
    nullable: true,
  })
  type: PlatformType;
```
